name: (All Seeing) Eye of the Beholder
description:
Resolution: 1080x1080
Format: h.264 mpeg .MP4
Bit-rate: 6-24 Mbps (VBR)
FPS: 30
Render Time: 10hrs

An abstract work with both beauty and clandestine undertones.

Self-modeled in 3D software, stop-motion animated, then brought into AFX for post-processing and finishing.

Decided to produce triangular bokeh to re-enforce the triangle theme.


Hope it is well received, but if not, have a lovely day regardless!
